    • behaviortree.graphBT.StyleUtil

  • public class StyleUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Styles are created here with "plain"-methods, i.e. all values have to be set explicitly. See chapters "Using Styles" and "Color Schemas" in tutorial for deatails.
